    <description>Auto closes cases that are non-target or are in the new status, assigned to a queue, and has had no stripe attempt count updates in over 10 days. Routes ACH failures into queue.
08/22/23 - PE - Updated flow to prevent auto-closing of cases when the school object was just moved to Free recently. (Sprint15 - 2023)
09/15/23 - PE - Added decision node to confirm the case&apos;s account has a school object (Sprint 17)
12/07/23 - PE - Updated Failed Payment case ownership to be RR between users inside the group Failed Payment Case Owners (Revenue.io Implementation)
04/11/24 - PE - Updated Premium Target Field. Added scheduled path to create Cancel Request cases.
04/18/24 - PE - Update flow to assign ownership of new case to account&apos;s SaaS Owner
05/02/24 - BW - Updated flow to populate Created Cancel Request Case lookup and not create a second Cancel Request Case on the immediate path
05/30/24 - PE - Added decision node to check if Stripe triggered the flow to update &apos;Stripe Attempt Count&apos; on a closed case/
07/15/24 - PE - Updated flow to not update case is it&apos;s closed
12/06/24 - LK - Before launching Account Assignment Subflow, the flow checks to see if the case created has an Account Id. Fixing flow errors where id var was null for the subflow.
01/10/25 - removing reference to Target Designation at Cancellation as a part of Project Ren / School Object field cleanup
06/12/25 - PE - Mapped Engagement Notes from FP case to new Cancel case using formula

Diagram: https://drive.google.com/file/d/17aUeL8xfcB_9vk2KnsBo3UeoBcZ5PW50/view?usp=sharing
3/11/25 JH: launch account ownership assignments decision node to also end if no contact id related to case</description>
    <environments>Default</environments>
    <formulas>
        <name>for_EngagementNotes</name>
        <dataType>String</dataType>
        <expression>IF(
  ISBLANK( {!$Record.Engagement_Notes__c}),
  &quot;No Engagement Notes from original FP case &quot; 
    &amp; {!$Record.CaseNumber} 
    &amp; &quot; on &quot; 
    &amp; TEXT( TODAY() ),
  &quot;Engagement Notes from original FP case &quot; 
    &amp; {!$Record.CaseNumber} 
    &amp; &quot; on &quot; 
    &amp; TEXT( TODAY() ) 
    &amp; &quot;:&quot;
    &amp; BR()
    &amp; MID(
        {!$Record.Engagement_Notes__c},
        1,
        32768 
          - LEN(
              &quot;Engagement Notes from original FP case &quot; 
                &amp; {!$Record.CaseNumber} 
                &amp; &quot; on &quot; 
                &amp; TEXT( TODAY() ) 
                &amp; BR()
            )
      )
)</expression>
    </formulas>
    <formulas>
        <name>forB_IsNew</name>
        <dataType>Boolean</dataType>
        <expression>ISNEW()</expression>
    </formulas>
    <formulas>
        <description>Checks whether the school object linked to the case&apos;s account has been recently switched to Free status.</description>
        <name>forB_RecentlyMovedtoFree</name>
        <dataType>Boolean</dataType>
        <expression>AND(
    OR({!$Record.Account.Ever_Premium_ECE__c}= TRUE, 
          {!$Record.Account.Current_Premium_ECE__c} = TRUE ),
{!$Record.Account.School_Object__r.Cancellation_Date__c} &gt;= TODAY() - 2)</expression>
    </formulas>
    <formulas>
        <name>forT_CancelCaseDescription</name>
        <dataType>String</dataType>
        <expression>IF(
{!$Flow.CurrentDate} - 7 &gt;= DATEVALUE({!$Record.CreatedDate}), {!texT_CancelCaseAutoCloseDescription}, 
IF(
{!$Record.Stripe_funding__c} = &quot;ACH Account&quot;,
{!texT_CancelCaseACHFailureDescription},
{!texT_CancelCaseManualCloseDescription}
)
)</expression>
    </formulas>
